S
m:2^S\to R
(a)
m(\varnothing) = 0
(b)
m
\forall A,B \in 2^S, A\subseteq B\Longrightarrow m(A)\le m(B)
\emptyset \cap \emptyset =\emptyset
m(\emptyset)
m(\emptyset)=m(\emptyset \cup \emptyset)=m(\emptyset)+ m(\emptyset) ,
0=m(\emptyset). 
m
A\subset B
(B\setminus A)\cap A=\emptyset
A\cup (B\setminus A)=B
m(B)=m((B\setminus A)\cup A)=m(B\setminus A)+m(A)\geq m(A), 
m(A)\leq m(B). 
